lyrics:
[verse]
Liška a lišák by the meadow danced
Feeding their little one, a fox cub so entranced
With carrot puree, the tastiest delight
They danced and played under the moonlight

[chorus]
Liška, lišák, and their fox cub too
Having the time of their lives, so true
With carrot puree, their hearts so high
In this funky groove, they'll forever fly
